  "1772910": {
    "name": "Dead District: Survival",
    "steam_appid": 1772910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772910/extras/6817ff8db46d8654e65932c315c6b93b.avif?t=1764922174\" width=600 height=152 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Dead District》</strong>是一款开放世界生存沙盒游戏，每一个决定都至关重要。你将从一座充满敌意的岛屿出发：野生动物、致命陷阱、感染者，以及为生存不择手段的幸存者随处可见。你的目标很简单——活下去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造庇护所，制作武器与工具，种植食物，独自或与朋友一同探索岛屿。提供四位独特的可操控角色，随时迎接生存挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772910/extras/39d0cb9d438f637b9152d2d2a8530182.avif?t=1764922174\" width=600 height=175 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多人模式中共享资源、保卫基地，或在单人模式中检验你的实力。驾驶载具、狩猎、完成任务，在这个不容犯错的世界里走出属于你的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 单人/多人生存模式</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 基地建造与制作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 动态天气与昼夜循环</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 任务与委托系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 农耕、狩猎与资源采集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 驾驶与战斗</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 四名可玩角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 危机四伏的广阔开放世界</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1772910/extras/215effeb9e44caec6b8e51e641f0deef.avif?t=1764922174\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
